MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

––––––––––––––––––––
If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

Bindr is the #1 Bisexual, LGBTQ+, Lesbian Dating App. Our app is designed for meeting other local couples and singles regardless of sexual preferences. By not requiring your sexual orientation, we’re open to everyone regardless if their bisexual, pansexual, lesbian, queer, gay or anyone looking for a better, fluid LGBTQ dating experience. So if you're looking for the perfect bisexual dating app, lesbian dating app or in general a LGBTQ dating app Bindr is the place for you!

Bindr is a queer dating app built by us, for us! We know first hand it can be hard to identify as bisexual, pansexual, lesbian, gay and anything in between so we don't ask those questions, love somebody for who they are, not who they love on Bindr. We're the "bi" umbrella of apps that fill in those gaps that were often times left out until now. Share as little or as much about your sexual identity and orientation as you'd like and find love for love.

Unlike other apps, we don’t want to put you into a box. We believe you should set your preferences the way you want and for that, we don’t give any priority to anyone based on their sexual preferences. This has helped us not only make an application inclusive of bisexual and pansexual people, but everyone regardless if you’re lesbian, trans, asexual, queer, poly, or similar.

Here’s a list of some of our awesome features:

1. Chat with anyone when you both like each other.
2 Premium members can message someone first without matching to send a request.
3. Geo-location preferences to find users near and far.
4. Community Timelines & Social Feeds
5. Active users show up first
6. Paid users can see who liked them.
7. Paid users can also see who’s been viewing them.

And so much more!

We’ve helped hundreds of thousands of people meet in under a year. We’re the fastest growing bisexual app and we care about making a difference for the communities we represent. It’s important to us to use our platform to provide resources back to those communities. We hope to use out platform to help break the silence of important issues such as biphobia, trans rights and by representing those who are often ignored in the LGBTQIA+ community and sending the message that it's always okay to be your true self.

Start your transformation today with ToneAI.

Quick Link is a comprehensive product that combines the functions of scanning and creating QR codes, aiming to provide users with a convenient and efficient QR code experience.

QR Code Scanning
Fast Recognition: Quick Link uses advanced image recognition technology to quickly and accurately scan and recognize the information in the QR code.
Multi-functional support: It supports scanning QR codes containing URL, text, phone number, SMS, email address and other information to meet the diversified needs of users.

QR Code Creation
Flexible editing: Users can customize the QR code with text, URL, contact information, etc. according to their needs.
One-click generation: After editing, users can simply click one-click generation to get their own QR code.

Efficient and Convenient
1. Quick Link's fast and accurate scanning and creation capability greatly improves users' efficiency in handling QR codes.
2. The simple and easy-to-use interface design makes it easy for users to get started without complicated operations.
Multi-functional Integration
1. Integrates scanning and creation functions to meet the needs of users in different scenarios.
2. supports the processing of QR codes of various information types to meet the diversified information interaction needs of users.
Secure and Reliable
1. adopts advanced encryption technology to ensure user information security.
2. Strict data protection mechanism ensures that user information will not be leaked or abused.

Turn your free time into real rewards by sharing your opinion! With our app you can participate in paid surveys and questionnaires on a wide variety of topics: technology, fashion, entertainment, sports, health, travel, food, current trends, and much more. Every answer you give is valuable, because companies and organizations around the world use this information to improve their products, services, and future decisions. Your opinion matters — and now it can also help you earn real rewards.

Why choose our surveys app? Because it combines the best of usability, rewards, and trust. Unlike other platforms that feel complicated or unreliable, here you will find a clear and intuitive experience from the very first moment. In just a few taps you can start answering surveys that are tailored to your interests, and every completed questionnaire brings you closer to redeeming rewards such as cash, PayPal payments, or gift cards from your favorite stores. 

Main Features:

● Personalized Surveys – Get access to questionnaires designed around your profile and preferences. If you love technology, you’ll receive tech-related surveys. If you’re into lifestyle or entertainment, you’ll see more questions in those categories. This personalization means your experience is always relevant and engaging.  
● Earn Real Rewards – Your time is valuable. That’s why every completed survey gives you points that you can redeem for real-world rewards. Choose between cash, PayPal, or popular gift cards to make the most of your participation.  
● Simple and Intuitive – No complicated menus or long registrations. The app is designed to be easy for everyone, so you can focus on giving your opinion without distractions.  
● Security and Privacy – Your personal data is protected and used only anonymously. Companies see aggregated information, never your identity. We respect your privacy as much as we value your input.  
● Make an Impact – Your answers are more than just data. They help brands, startups, and organizations understand what consumers really want. This way, you’re contributing to better products and services that improve everyday life.  
● Wide Variety of Topics – From new apps and gadgets to lifestyle, health, sports, or even global issues, you’ll always find fresh and interesting surveys waiting for you.  

With our app, you’re not just filling in questionnaires: you’re becoming part of a global community of opinion leaders. Millions of people worldwide are already using surveys to shape the future of the products and services they use every day. Now it’s your turn to join them.

Getting started is simple: download the app, and start answering your first survey today. The more you participate, the faster you’ll accumulate points and the sooner you’ll redeem your rewards. Whether you want a little extra pocket money, a PayPal transfer, or a gift card for shopping online, this app gives you the flexibility to choose what suits you best.

Don’t let your opinions go unheard. Start turning them into rewards right now. By using our app, you’re not only helping brands improve, but also enjoying tangible benefits in return. The combination of simplicity, security, and real payouts makes it the ideal platform for anyone who wants to make the most of their time.  

Download now, join the community, and discover how easy it is to earn money and rewards simply by answering surveys. Your opinion is powerful — let it work for you!

ClockPhone is a stylish and functional clock app that’s easy to use.

It features an advanced alarm with flexible repeat settings: by day of the week, on a specific date, or following a shift schedule. And to make sure you really wake up, there are not just standard options to turn it off, but also advanced methods — like scanning an NFC tag, QR/barcode (for example, on a toothpaste tube in the bathroom), or solving math problems.

ClockPhone also includes a versatile timer, perfect for workouts — including various interval types like Tabata, and productivity techniques like Pomodoro, 52/17, and 90/30 — as well as for cooking, meditation, and any task that needs precise time control.

The app combines a thoughtfully designed interface with a rich feature set. Thanks to its stylish and attractive time display, ClockPhone fits beautifully into any space. The large digits are easy to read from any distance, and the second hand comes with different display modes for enhanced readability. Time transitions are smoothly animated, and the clock’s appearance is easy to customize via a functional and intuitive interface.
